Before/ after and maybe someday it will be after/before... here is another example of how gender is a force that is constantly shifting and evolving, in the same way that every part of our being is changing throughout our lives. I have always felt in-between genders, even as a child, growing up in the 80s, when I didn’t have any kind of language or modelling for what that could look like. Well as it turns out, it looks like me 🖤 PS: getting my drivers license at age 36 was one of the best decisions I ever made 💅💅💅 #nevertooold

Hey all! We’ve got gorgeous Perverts Against Pipelines t-shirts for sale in our new boutique! ***All proceeds go the the Unist’ot’en Legal Defence Fund*** Support Indigenous Land Defenders today and come by @catalpastudio and get yours!  We have hoodies, sweatshirts, long-sleeves and t-shirts in a limited selection of sizes and colours. If there is demand we can order more variety of colour and size. Shirts are priced on a sliding scale- enquire for exact pricing of each model. We are also open to shipping shirts to those outside of Montreal. If you don’t want a shirt but want to donate directly to the Unist’ot’en Legal Defence Fund you can do so via this link: https://actionnetwork.org/fundraising/unistoten2020legalfund/
🖤🖤🖤
Les t-shirts Pervert Against Pipelines sont en vente à notre nouvelle boutique ***L’argent sera reversé en totalité au fond de défense juridique d’Unist’ot’en*** Supportez  les Wet'suwet'en qui défendent les terres et territoires autochtones  et venez au @catalpastudio pour avoir le votre! Nous avons des hoodies, sweatshirts, des t-shirts manches longues et manches courtes dans une sélection limitée de tailles et de couleurs. Si il y a assez de demande nous pouvons  commander une plus large variété de tailles et de couleurs. Le prix des vêtements se fait sur une échelle de prix -nous contacter pour connaître le prix de chaque modèle. Nous pouvons aussi les envoyer pour les personnes qui sont en dehors de Montréal. Si vous ne voulez pas de t-shirts mais voulez donner directement au fond de défense juridique d'Unist'ot'en, vous pouvez le faire via ce lien: 
https://actionnetwork.org/fundraising/unistoten2020legalfund/

They’re here!!! We are so excited @catalpastudio to begin our transition to using biodegradable/ compostable tattoo supplies, starting with biodegradable gloves from the excellent Toronto- based @goodjudy.ca. In the coming months we look forward to replacing our razors and plastic hygienic products with biodegradable razors and barrier film.
Other goals to reduce the waste we produce at Catalpa:
-donate paper scraps to a local paper making company
-turn our full page paper waste into hand-made books
-using compostable garbage bags
Other actions we are taking to support climate justice:
-starting this week there will be “Perverts Against Pipelines” t-shirts for sale in our little boutique. All profits from their sales will go to the Unist’ot’en Legal Defence fund which needs our support more than ever. 
Thanks for your ongoing support of our little endeavour 🖤 .
